title: EP051 FEATURING WAKA FLOCKA
description:
On this episode of Million Dollaz Worth of Game, Waka Flocka speaks about Atlanta being the number 1 music spot, being faithful in a room full of hoes, the music business, Gucci Mane collaboration & much more!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/mworthofgame
